      <title>债券市场认为通胀有跌破美联储目标的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bond-market-sees-danger-of-inflation-falling-below-fed-s-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储抗击通胀已经两年了，债券投资者看到了一个新的风险：消费者价格降温过快。]]></description>
