    <item>
      <title>高盛的股票模型对 ESG 假设提出了挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/goldman-has-a-stock-model-that-s-challenging-esg-assumptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 设有 ESG 过滤器，告知投资者购买煤炭巨头嘉能可 (Glencore Plc) 的股票，并避开大型科技股微软 (Microsoft Corp.) 和 Alphabet Inc.。]]></description>
