      <title>收购公司 GTCR 正就收购德国制药商 Stada 进行深入谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/gtcr-is-said-in-advanced-talks-to-buy-german-drugmaker-stada</link>
