      <title>供应过剩担忧加剧 布伦特原油跌破 70 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brent-oil-tumbles-below-70-as-oversupply-fears-deepen-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布伦特原油期货价格两年多来首次跌破每桶 70 美元，受供应充足、需求担忧和投机性抛售猖獗的影响，油价再次下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brent-oil-tumbles-below-70-as-oversupply-fears-deepen-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Oneok 发行 70 亿美元债券以支付收购费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/oneok-to-sell-bonds-for-enlink-midstream-interest-purchases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，Oneok Inc. 开始发售投资级债券。不到两周前，这家管道公司宣布将收购一家竞争对手和另一家公司的控股权，交易总额达 59 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/oneok-to-sell-bonds-for-enlink-midstream-interest-purchases</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 13:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
